column2: "Fhm! You foolish fools! If you want to beat me, you're going to need a hundred times more people!"
"Alright this what I'll say. It's not embarrassing at all!"
"Oh, you! Did you hear my amazing victory speech?"
"Your victory cry is really important. When the battle is over you need to let everyone know how cool you are!"
"Doing what feels good is most important! There isn't anyone who goes out of their way to do something they hate!"
"If there is nothing good after a battle, then does fighting really have any meaning? That's why you need to act cool!"
"Being cool is the most important thing, and justice is cool."
"Now if you'll excuse me, I need to keep spreading justice! May we meet again!"
